---
// src/pages/index.astro
// This is your minimal, professional B2B "Pro" site.
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Sovereign Systems | Digital Fortresses</title>

    <style>
      :root {
        --color-bg: #111111;
        --color-text: #EAEAEA;
        --color-accent: #007BFF; /* A professional blue */
        --color-border: #333;
      }
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto,
          Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        color: var(--color-text);
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      main {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        padding: 0 1rem;
      }
      h1, h2 {
        color: var(--color-text);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        padding-bottom: 10px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .tiers {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      .tier {
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background-color: #191919;
      }
      .tier h3 {
        color: var(--color-accent);
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
      .tier ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .tier li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: var(--color-accent);
        color: #FFFFFF;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Sovereign Systems</h1>
      <p>
        We build digital fortresses. We are a private, high-end consulting
        service for business owners who require robust, sovereign, and
        automated systems.
      </p>

      <h2>Retainer Tiers</h2>
      <div class="tiers">
        
        <div class="tier">
          <h3>Tier 1: The Sentinel</h3>
          <p>$1,000 / month</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Monthly Vulnerability Scans</li>
            <li>SaaS Stack & Cost Audit</li>
            <li>"State of Sovereignty" Report</li>
            <li>Quarterly Advisory Call</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="tier">
          <h3>Tier 2: The Guardian</h3>
          <p>$2,500 / month</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Everything in "Sentinel"</li>
            <li><strong>Active Vulnerability Remediation</strong></li>
            <li>Privacy Hardening (VPN, Comms)</li>
            <li><strong>1-2 Custom n8n Workflow Builds</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="tier">
          <h3>Tier 3: The Fortress</h3>
          <p>$5,000+ / month</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Everything in "Guardian"</li>
            <li><strong>Full-Spectrum AI/Automation</strong></li>
            <li>Ongoing Threat Monitoring</li>
            <li>24/7 Incident Response</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <section style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <h2>Book a Consultation</h2>
        <p>
          All B2B engagements begin with a non-invasive scan and a private
          consultation.
        </p>
        <a
          href="[TALLY_FORM_D_LINK]"
          class="btn"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Request a Consultation
        </a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
